001cdf0908129b2ee0935762a73","tid":1222873,"uid":12208,"like":225,"dislike":3,"score":222,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"處長話我係警察就係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc43154a827dcc2c3695a00c1078cabedd87f1d2","tid":1222873,"uid":98920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccfecdc9210288ecf6609be1472f3076bc085087","tid":1222873,"uid":47265,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"並受該職級的一切紀律條文所規限。 <br />\n<br />\n啫係都要有PASS"},{"pid":"150ed63dd92432ad4256099673620a5e7a8d6a7e","tid":1222873,"uid":191701,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:37.000Z","msg":"新香港人抄散"},{"pid":"74dc017c068d7ccbb50af491ccae171eec098343","tid":1222873,"uid":112467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"屌撚左出聲"},{"pid":"dba0e03dad3d73e8560080ea131e7d6ec634e5cb","tid":1222873,"uid":125026,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"仲有基要服務團同特務警察<br />\n<br />\n「梁美芬的建議確有法律依據，根據香港法例第197章《基要服務團條例》，特首可招募基要服務團團員，他們於被動員作現役服務時，與警隊成員有相同的權力，和具有與警隊成員相同的特權、保障及豁免權。此條例的立法原意，為上世紀五十年代警力不足，故依例授權新界村長等人拘捕疑犯，再交予警方，今天香港已有大量輔警，此法例只屬備而不用。<br />\n<br />\n更少人提及的是香港法例第245章《公安條例》的第四十至四十三條，特首可委任特務警察，任期由特首在命令中指明。特務警察與警務人員的職責、權力、保障及豁免權相同。「特務警察」原出於太平洋戰爭前夕，殖民地政府另行招募人手，令警隊可輔助香港防務。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20140707/bkn-20140707000218580-0707_00832_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcommentary%2F20140707%2Fbkn-20140707000218580-0707_00832_001.html&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2ef9d7c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20140707/bkn-20140707000218580-0707_00832_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"373eeba68a1619bbd6c89cf673e79bb9c9c2844a","tid":1222873,"uid":175036,"like":121,"dislike":1,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"打記者違反公約就話唔知<br />\nHeadshot違反武力使用指引又話唔知<br />\n明正言順請外援做乜夠膽做唔夠膽認呀？<br />\n唔係好鐘意玩白色恐怖架咩<br />\n直接話「呀sir請人唔使你教」就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d81a9168d63e60895568073705d5636ce71cfc","tid":1222873,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f83395e3e330f4008c88186002458eb55a76eaa","tid":1222873,"uid":94774,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實依樣野係咪需要提出修例<br />\n已過時"},{"pid":"0e0fa5515688d4a749135767dbff2546a9dafd01","tid":1222873,"uid":175036,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"2f83395e3e330f4008c88186002458eb55a76eaa","tid":1222873,"uid":94774,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實依樣野係咪需要提出修例<br />\n已過時"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"香港過時條例一大堆<br />\n對政權有利嘅點會搞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a90d4168098494eeed72ff0e9c47c96a3413eb","tid":1222873,"uid":96146,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"做狗都有得炒散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6527b7c02587170b9be38032ab939fed7887c7f9","tid":1222873,"uid":102078,"like":259,"dislike":1,"score":258,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"習近平：「這是正式錄用的警察嗎？！<br />\n屌,習大大原來一早知班仆街有演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94b9e97e048ff038437d42836a2589d606c942c","tid":1222873,"uid":69866,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"任何人包唔包解放軍？俾